headline: Nayya Partners with Paychex to Empower Workforces with AI-Driven Benefits
summary: Nayya, the leading AI-powered benefits optimization platform, today announced a strategic partnership with Paychex, Inc., a leading provider of human capital management (HCM) solutions, to deliver personalized benefits guidance at scale. Through this collaboration, Nayya's connected data and intelligence are embedded in the Paychex experience, giving employees a clearer, more personalized way to understand, navigate, and make the most of their benefits.
